Package com.example.demo.model

Class Orders

java.lang.Object
com.example.demo.model.Orders
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Entity public class Orders extends Object implements Serializable
Represents an order placed by a user. This class contains information about the order such as the order date, total price, order ID, list of dishes, and the user who placed the order.

The fields are annotated with JPA annotations for ORM mapping. Lombok annotations are used to generate boilerplate code like getters, setters, and constructors.
